				"string" : "GitHub tells me that it has been 1.5 years, a bit over 700 commits, and around 15,000 lines of code since I’ve started work on [gt4llm](https://github.com/feenkcom/gt4llm), the Large Language Model workbench inside Glamorous Toolkit. Time truly flies."
