				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I’ve written about my work on gt4llm a bit [here](https://blog.veitheller.de/LlmL.html), and I won’t be doing that again. I promised a more philosophical blog post, and this is my attempt at doing so."
