				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "zYoO/3LyDQCpEzLFCBR5Zw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I want to talk about something much deeper than LLMs and their whimsical implementations, something that begins before we talk about any technological consideration, though it informs it. I want to talk about how I see most people using LLMs, and why I think they’re doing it wrong, and how they could do it better. I also want to talk about why LLMs work differently than people think they do."
			},
