				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "As a disclaimer: I heavily use em-dashes and always have. Still, I want to assert that this should not be taken to mean that this article has been written by a machine. It would have probably done a better job, as I’m a terrible waffler."
